responses.message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I doubt you can help me. Your company is a mess!
I'm here to help. Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for completing security. Can you also confirm your date of birth?
That's all correct. Can you please provide me with your first line of address and postcode?
Great, thank you for confirming. Can you confirm your email address as well?
Thank you for completing security. I'm sorry to hear that you're facing difficulties. How can I assist you today?
I need help with a claim that your company has not processed yet. It's been weeks!
I understand the frustration. Let me look into this for you. Please allow me a moment to check your account.
Take your time. I've been waiting long enough.
Thank you for your patience. It seems there was a delay in processing your claim. A possible resolution could be expediting the review process. Does this work for you?
Yes, that would be great. I appreciate your help on this.
Glad we could help. I will escalate this issue for you. Is there anything else you need assistance with today?
No, that's all sorted. Thank you for your help.
You're welcome. If you have any further questions in the future, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
